---

<section
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-[#262626] text-[#e5e5e5] overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-20">
        <svg class="w-full h-full">
            <filter id="scratches">
                <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.8" numOctaves="3"></feTurbulence>
                <feColorMatrix type="saturate" values="0"></feColorMatrix>
            </filter>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#404040" filter="url(#scratches)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                <span
                    class="text-[#a3a3a3] font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-[#525252] pb-2"
                    >¿Quién Raya a Quién?</span
                >
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif italic text-white">La Escala de Mohs</h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-serif text-[#d4d4d4]/90">
                    No puedes medir la dureza apretando. Tienes que destruir. Friedrich Mohs
                    organizó el mundo mineral en una pelea de patio de colegio.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="bg-[#171717]/60 p-6 rounded-sm border border-[#404040] mt-4 backdrop-blur-sm"
                >
                    <h3 class="text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold mb-2">Del Talco al Diamante</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#a3a3a3] leading-relaxed">
                        Si A raya a B, A es más duro. Simple. Tu uña (2.5) raya el yeso (2). El
                        cuarzo (7) raya el vidrio (5.5).
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#d4d4d4] italic">
                        El diamante (10) era el rey invicto, hasta que empezamos a crear materiales
                        que ni la naturaleza imaginó.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center relative h-[400px]">
                <div class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" class="w-full h-full overflow-visible">
                        <rect
                            x="50"
                            y="100"
                            width="300"
                            height="150"
                            fill="#525252"
                            stroke="#737373"
                            stroke-width="2"></rect>
                        <text
                            x="200"
                            y="280"
                            text-anchor="middle"
                            fill="#a3a3a3"
                            font-family="monospace">MUESTRA (DUREZA 5)</text
                        >

                        <path
                            d="M 60 120 L 150 140"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#262626"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.5"></path>
                        <path
                            d="M 70 200 L 120 180"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#262626"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.5"></path>

                        <g class="animate-scratch-move">
                            <rect x="-5" y="-60" width="10" height="60" fill="#a3a3a3"></rect>

                            <path d="M 0 0 L -5 -10 L 5 -10 Z" fill="#bbf7d0"></path>

                            <circle
                                cx="0"
                                cy="0"
                                r="15"
                                fill="white"
                                opacity="0"
                                class="animate-scratch-spark"></circle>
                        </g>

                        <path
                            d="M 100 150 L 300 150"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#e5e5e5"
                            stroke-width="3"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-dasharray="200"
                            stroke-dashoffset="200"
                            class="animate-draw-scratch"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes scratchMove {
        0% {
            transform: translate(100px, 150px) rotate(-10deg);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translate(300px, 150px) rotate(-10deg);
        }
        100% {
            transform: translate(300px, 150px) rotate(-10deg);
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-scratch-move {
        animation: scratchMove 2s ease-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes drawScratch {
        0% {
            stroke-dashoffset: 200;
        }
        50% {
            stroke-dashoffset: 0;
        }
        100% {
            stroke-dashoffset: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-draw-scratch {
        animation: drawScratch 2s ease-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scratchSpark {
        0%,
        10% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.5);
        }
        25% {
            opacity: 0.8;
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.5);
        }
    }
    .animate-scratch-spark {
        animation: scratchSpark 2s ease-out infinite;
    }
</style>
